resources.string: Kra n yisnasen ur zmiren ara ad ttwakksen ɣef sebba n tlisa n unagraw, acukan tzemreḍ ad teffreḍ tignitin-nsen akken ur tent-twaliḍ ara.
Mdel leqjer n usnas deg ulday n usnas
Awiǧit meqqer aṭas i teɣzi n ugdil agejdan amiran
Asexsi n usireg anedbal ad yekkes asiti-nni s snat n tikkal akken ad yeskweṛ tmahilt n ugdil.
Sit aɣezfan ɣef uwiǧit, syin zuɣer-it deg ugdil-ik-im agejdan
Sken s wudem awurman anasiw deg leqjer
Sit snat n tikkal akken ad tsekkṛeḍ agdil
Akken ad tremdeḍ asiti n snat tikal i tmahilt n usekkeṛ n ugdil, yessefk ad tged assireg n unebdal. Ger tamawt dakken asnas-nni ur yezmir ara ad yettwakkes arma yettwakkes ussireg-a.
